  <brief_title>Measurement of Cerebral and Peripheric Tissue Oxygenation in Anemic Preterm Infants Who Underwent Blood Transfusion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Measurement of Cerebral and Peripheric Tissue Oxygenation in Anemic Preterm Infants Who Underwent Blood Transfusion:A Near Infrared Spectroscopy Study.</official_title>
